node.text: Jesus. Looking back at 365 days ago I was nervous as hell looking at my phone praying that y’all would love my baby @laidbylira just as much as I do And we sold out! I was amazed. This experience was definitely one for the books and I’ll do it again in a heart beat. Watch as we take you on a journey of opening Laid By Lira. Shop @laidbylira today! 20% off using code Anniversary and we have $40 Kits as well only a couple more hours for this sale. Thank you to @director_emc @skrptz @c.a.l.m__visualz for documenting this journey for me. Part TWO coming soon.
